{"tid":155252,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]支那神劇將會由3個香港藝員擔正主角","createTime":"2017-03-14T01:06:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-20T05:09:05.000Z","uid":54373,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cf34dd5c4f7c6f8ed982608d8e1328a60cf6a6f5","tid":155252,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:06:13.000Z","msg":"咩玩法？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n藝人麥長青（麥包）獲肇慶市政府邀請出席在當地舉行的「包公誕」傳統民俗活動，與現場大批市民齊齊以傳統方式紀念包公，祈求國泰民安、風調雨順。 <br />\n<br />\n而當地負責人正與麥包洽談拍攝40集電視劇《包青天》，很大機會<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">由麥包擔演這位宋代廉潔偉人包拯，據知劇組亦希望邀得樊少皇及陳浩民分別扮演展昭及公孫策</span></span>，主辦方希望透過復辦包公誕及開拍劇集，弘揚清廉公正精神。"},{"pid":"800b642f2bb035acbae7fc8f2f6525844e8bcab6","tid":155252,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:08:17.000Z","msg":"包青天 - 麥包 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n展昭 - 范少蝗 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n公孫賊 - 陳浩民<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bfabdc975fd7315534c7047cd627afdb6bb5080b","tid":155252,"uid":44916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:19:09.000Z","msg":"麥包青天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96a270875380e563d3d2aedecac94b60f40c8540","tid":155252,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:22:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>麥包青天<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f3f2201bb34657b3ad734c12f9f48c29689636b3","tid":155252,"uid":57705,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-14T01:28:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"204a4ddc23152ccae4e027667829909c38cb7df7","tid":155252,"uid":51753,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime